    "## Example Walkthrough\n",
    "\n",
    "Suppose image: A dog sitting beside a bicycle\n",
    "\n",
    "* Input: `800×800`\n",
    "* Selective Search: `2000 proposals`\n",
    "      ```text\n",
    "      R1: dog area\n",
    "      R2: bicycle area\n",
    "      R3: sky\n",
    "      R4: grass\n",
    "      ```\n",
    "3. Whole image: `800×800` passes through CNN:\n",
    "      * Feature map:\n",
    "            $$\n",
    "            50×50×512\n",
    "            $$\n",
    "\n",
    "4. ROI projection:\n",
    "      ```text\n",
    "      R1→feature map region\n",
    "      R2→feature map region\n",
    "      ```\n",
    "5. ROI pooling:\n",
    "      ```text\n",
    "      R1→7×7×512\n",
    "      R2→7×7×512\n",
    "      ```\n",
    "\n",
    "6. Classification:\n",
    "      ```text\n",
    "      R1:\n",
    "      Dog=.98\n",
    "      Bike=.01\n",
    "\n",
    "      R2:\n",
    "      Dog=.02\n",
    "      Bike=.95\n",
    "      ```\n",
    "7. Bounding box refinement:\n",
    "      ```text\n",
    "      Dog box adjusted\n",
    "      Bike box adjusted\n",
    "      ```\n",
    "8. Final result:\n",
    "      ```text\n",
    "      Dog      [x1,y1,x2,y2]\n",
    "      Bicycle  [x1,y1,x2,y2]\n",
    "      ```\n",
    "\n",
    "## Charecterstics\n",
    "\n",
    "### Why Fast R-CNN Is Faster\n",
    "\n",
    "R-CNN:\n",
    "\n",
    "* 2000 proposals\n",
    "* →2000 CNN computations\n",
    "\n",
    "Fast R-CNN:\n",
    "\n",
    "* 1 image\n",
    "* 1 CNN computation\n",
    "\n",
    "Feature maps are reused.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Speed Comparison\n",
    "\n",
    "Approximate values:\n",
    "\n",
    "| Method     |  Training |   Test Speed |\n",
    "| ---------- | --------: | -----------: |\n",
    "| R-CNN      | Very slow |  ~47 s/image |\n",
    "| Fast R-CNN |    Faster | ~0.3 s/image |\n",
    "\n",
    "Huge improvement.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Advantages\n",
    "\n",
    "1. Shared computation: CNN runs once.\n",
    "2. End-to-end learning: Single-stage optimization.\n",
    "3. Better accuracy: Joint optimization improves results.\n",
    "4. No feature storage\n",
    "      * R-CNN stored CNN features on disk.\n",
    "      * Fast R-CNN computes features directly.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Limitations\n",
    "\n",
    "Fast R-CNN still uses: Selective Search\n",
    "      * Selective Search itself is slow: `≈2 seconds/image`\n",
    "\n",
    "Even though CNN became fast, proposal generation remained a bottleneck.\n",
    "\n",
    "This limitation led to the development of Faster R-CNN, which replaced Selective Search with a Region Proposal Network (RPN).\n",
    "\n",
    "### Comparison: R-CNN vs Fast R-CNN\n",
    "\n",
    "| Feature          | R-CNN            | Fast R-CNN       |\n",
    "| ---------------- | ---------------- | ---------------- |\n",
    "| CNN runs         | 2000 times       | 1 time           |\n",
    "| Classifier       | SVM              | Softmax          |\n",
    "| Training         | Multi-stage      | End-to-end       |\n",
    "| Feature storage  | Required         | Not required     |\n"
   ]
